    dc:description "Fig. 2. Collecting localities of Crenicichla lacustris and C. mucuryna in the coastal rivers of eastern Brazil. Mostimportant rivers are:1. Rio Paraíba do Sul; 2. RioDoce; and 3. Rio Jequitinhonha.A symbol may cover more than one collecting site." ;
